  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study has to show that an intubation with the AuraGain Laryngeal mask could bring the
      same benefits in terms of intubation in clinical practice, as the slotted Guedel tubus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
